## Recommended Actions

### Digital
1. **Move redemption preference to top-level rewards settings (1 tap from dashboard) and add 'Set as default' option for auto-redemption.** — Rewards & Loyalty — Reduces ~7 calls (43.8%)
2. **Show MCC code and category assigned to each transaction, allow flagging incorrect categorization, and clearly list category bonus exclusions.** — Rewards & Loyalty — Reduces ~3 calls (18.8%)
3. **Add real-time welcome bonus spend tracker on the rewards dashboard with progress bar and days remaining, and list qualifying/non-qualifying purchase categories clearly.** — Rewards & Loyalty — Reduces ~2 calls (12.5%)
4. **Show tier progress bar with exact spend needed for retention/upgrade and send 90/30-day tier expiry warnings.** — Rewards & Loyalty — Reduces ~1 calls (6.3%)

